{"title": "ONLINE: 38. Jahrestagung der European Society of Paediatric Infectious Diseases (ESPID), Rotterdam 2020", "author": null, "url": "https://dgpi.de/event/38-jahrestagung-der-european-society-of-paediatric-infectious-diseases-espid-rotterdam-2020/", "hostname": "dgpi.de", "description": "Update: This year's meeting will take place online only 38th Annual Meeting of the European Society for Paediatric Infectious Diseases (ESPID 2020) The organization of the meeting is a joint effort of ESPID members from the Netherlands. The ESPID forms the basis for investigators interested in infectious diseases in children and infection prevention in childhood.", "sitename": "DGPI: Deutsche Gesellschaft f\u00fcr P\u00e4diatrische Infektiologie", "date": "2020-10-26", "id": null, "license": null, "body": null, "comments": "", "commentsbody": null, "raw_text": null, "text": "Update: This year\u2019s meeting will take place online only\n38th Annual Meeting of the European Society for Paediatric Infectious Diseases (ESPID 2020)\nThe organization of the meeting is a joint effort of ESPID members from the Netherlands. The ESPID forms the basis for investigators interested in infectious diseases in children and infection prevention in childhood. As organizing committee we strongly feel that to further advance in our field it is pivotal to connect to adjacent disciplines. Therefore our main intent is to bring together the most prominent researchers in and relevant to the field of paediatric infectious diseases and immunology. Our meeting will provide an excellent opportunity to exchange knowledge and generate new ideas in a relaxed, smart albeit casual atmosphere. We believe the host city of Rotterdam is an ideal venue to achieve these goals. The city is easily accessible and has an excellent congress venue in the city centre close to convenient hotel facilities and vibrant restaurants and bars. Bring your research results and ideas to Rotterdam and join us to interact with fellow PID friends and colleagues from around the world. We will balance the outstanding scientific programme with fruitful social and networking activities.\nVirtual #ESPID2020: What to Expect\n- Watch all the sessions you are interested in \u2013 live or recorded\n- Earn the maximum CME credits by visiting all relevant lectures\n- Browse the research presentations and e-posters, and discuss them with their authors\n- Ask your questions and interact live with the PID experts, international colleagues, and industry representatives", "language": null, "image": "https://dgpi.de/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/dgpi_logo_175.png", "pagetype": "article", "links": ["#content", "https://dgpi.de/", "https://dgpi.de/", "https://dgpi.de/ueber-uns/", "https://dgpi.de/ueber-uns/", "https://dgpi.de/ueber-uns/geschaeftsstelle/", "https://dgpi.de/ueber-uns/vorstand/", "https://dgpi.de/ueber-uns/ausschuesse/", "https://dgpi.de/ueber-uns/mitgliedschaft/", "https://dgpi.de/ueber-uns/satzung/", "https://dgpi.de/ueber-uns/geschichte/", "https://dgpi.de/ueber-uns/ehrenmitglieder/", "https://dgpi.de/ueber-uns/historie-jahrestagungen/", "https://dgpi.de/ueber-uns/infektiologische-intensivkurse/", "https://dgpi.de/ueber-uns/english/", "https://dgpi.de/aktuelles/", "https://dgpi.de/aktuelles/", "https://dgpi.de/aktuelles/news/", "https://dgpi.de/aktuelles/infektiologie-news/", "https://dgpi.de/aktuelles/survey-news/", "https://dgpi.de/aktuelles/news-archiv/", "https://dgpi.de/events/", "https://dgpi.de/events/", "https://dgpi.de/events/kategorie/dgpi-veranstaltungen/list", "https://dgpi.de/events/kategorie/andere-veranstaltungen/", "https://dgpi.de/events/list/?tribe_paged=1&tribe_event_display=past", "https://dgpi.de/forschung/", "https://dgpi.de/forschung/", "https://dgpi.de/forschung/forschungsprojekte/", "https://dgpi.de/forschung/forschungsfoerderung/", "https://dgpi.de/forschung/stipendien/", "https://dgpi.de/forschung/vortrags-und-posterpreise/", "https://dgpi.de/forschung/forschungslandkarte/"